parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description: The language in which you want to display the results. Valid values: zh and en. zh indicates Chinese, which is the default value. en indicates English.

parameters.name: AhasNamespace
parameters.description: The namespace (environment) of Application High Availability Service (AHAS).

parameters.name: IsAHASPublicRegion
parameters.description: Specifies whether AHAS is deployed in the Internet region.

parameters.name: MseAppName
parameters.description: The name of the MSE application after migration. If this parameter is not specified, the name of the Application High Availability Service (AHAS) application is used by default.
